# Random Quote of the Day

Random Quote of the Day is an API for allowing consumers to view quotes and to save their favourite quotes for viewing later.

## Quotes [/quotes]

### List Quotes [GET /quotes/{?previous}{?latest}{?favourites}]

+ Parameters

    + previous: `true` (bool, optional) - Whether to return quotes from previous days only.
    + latest: `true` (bool, optional) - Whether to return quotes from previous days only.
    + favourites: `true` (bool, optional) - Whether to return the logged in user's favourite quotes only.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "data": [
                {
                    "id": 959,
                    "isOpen": false,
                    "formattedDate": "12th Nov 2020",
                    "author": {
                        "authorName": "Leonardo DiCaprio",
