## Favourites [/favourites]

### Create a New Favourite [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "user_id": 1234,
            "quote_id": 1234
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /quotes/1234

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1234,
                "isOpen": false,
                "formattedDate": "12th Nov 2020",
